    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Queuing at the post office to collect a parcel does not suspend your standard. Demand exactness from your everyday clothing. Anchor your mornings in dense cotton drill and crisp poplin. Ensure your metallic hardware stays cool and sharply reflective. Read the garment quality blindly. Window displays manipulate context, but physical mass gives an objective report. Reject lazy tailoring entirely. Maintain your rule across every item. Your baseline relies on clean geometry + hidden depth + one polished signal.",
