    "hardware_stones": {
      "text": "Seek out {stone_1} and {stone_2} for their sharp structural lines and clean geometry. Hold the piece in your palm to evaluate its density. The concentration of stone provides the only reliable metric. Search for a solid, cool centre. Avoid highly reflective hardware. This creates a harsh, distracting glare against your muted garments. Stick to brushed or matt settings to keep the look entirely cohesive. This strategy provides the hidden depth required to anchor your collection.",
