    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Lift the piece off the counter and weigh it in your palm. Physical density must match the visual scale of the object. Anchor your wardrobe with clean geometry that pulls firmly downward. Polished metallic finishes create a jarring glare against muted, cool fabrics. Choose a brushed or matt {metal_1} instead. This textural control supplies the hidden depth required to keep your style cohesive. Let the quiet substance of a {stone_1} speak through its true weight, rather than relying on a surface reflection.",
