    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your sweet spot lives exactly where {sweet_spot_keyword_1} meets {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Seek out materials like {texture_good_1} that deliver profound softness while holding an architectural edge. Gauge the structural memory of a garment by folding the collar or pleating the hem in your grip. When you release it, the material must spring back instantly rather than flattening into a shapeless heap. Judge this equilibrium strictly through touch. Every item must possess enough density to stand alone, establishing a cool boundary without feeling rigid.",
