    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, clean geometry dictates the uniform. Start with a stark navy worsted wool blazer. Look for straight lapels and padded shoulders. Let light movement act as the counterweight. Select a crisp cotton poplin shirt that sits lightly over the skin. Keep the details sparse. Fasten a cool silver watch around your wrist. Walking to the local shop for a sandwich demands the exact same standard as presenting a quarterly review. Trust your physical reactions. If a sleeve binds your arm when you reach for a folder, discard the item. Garments on a hanger look impeccable, but restriction in the shoulder exposes poor tailoring.",
