      "text": "In dim, close-quarters settings, let light movement lead your choices. A fine ribbed merino knit catches subtle shadows in any cool environment. Maintain your baseline standards across all hours. A private dinner requires the same worsted wool trousers you wore at your desk. Reject the trap of softening your shape for private events. Evaluate a piece by its drape in shadows. A dense, matt textile absorbs low light flawlessly. Select an icy grey colour. Keep jewellery strictly minimal. Add just a solitary white gold ring to provide a precise glint. Establish clean geometry in your tailoring to definitively set your outline.",
