    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Routine errands demand strict discipline. Reach for stark navy technical nylon trousers instead of worn joggers when leaving the house. Pair them with an icy grey fine ribbed merino jumper. Keep your focus on your core equation. Every daytime look must maintain clean geometry + light movement + one polished signal. Anchor the uniform with a cool silver zip or a rhodium watch dial to provide that required flash of reflection against matt textiles. Feel the tension in the seams as you bend. Your muscles know immediately when a cut restricts your stride. Let this direct tactile feedback guide your choices before stepping outside.",
