    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let cool composure lead your choices at work. Build around this calm centre using clean geometry in icy grey worsted wool to frame the body. Add a single mirror chrome watch or a sleek stark navy leather tote to deliver your one polished signal. Apply the desk test to every outfit. If sitting motionless at a keyboard makes you notice a pinching waistband or a riding sleeve, take the garment off. Refuse to endure physical restriction for a visual reward. Grasp the collar in your hands. If a heavy seam requires constant readjustment during a long meeting, eliminate the piece entirely.",
