    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your ideal pairing sits strictly between {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Anchor this base using {texture_good_1}. You are constructing clean geometry across your silhouette. Test every item yourself. Clench a handful of cloth at the hem. Open your fingers. If sharp folds stay stamped in the weave, walk away. The cloth must spring back smooth. This instant recovery prevents a collapsed shape. Combine this crisp structure with cool elements to finish the outfit.",
