    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let clean geometry lead your approach to the office. Support these sharp lines by maintaining a cool composure in your posture. Rely on icy grey worsted wool trousers and a stark navy shirt cut from crisp cotton poplin. Build your base layers from fine ribbed merino. Finish the look with a single steel watch to provide your one polished signal. Do not abandon this strict structure when the shift ends. Even a freezing midnight run to the petrol station demands a deliberate silhouette. Notice how technical nylon holds its rigid form in damp weather. Trust your physical instinct to gauge a garment. True structure reveals itself in motion, not reflections.",
