    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Weigh the piece in your palm. Gravity provides the most accurate assessment. Authentic metal sinks into the hand with a deliberate drag. Reject antiqued treatments, hammered textures, and artificially aged alloys. They register as clutter against crisp fabrics. Keep exclusively to highly polished {metal_1} or a perfectly set {stone_1}. This strict discipline preserves your clean geometry. A single gleaming detail acts as your one polished signal, anchoring the garment without shouting.",
