    },
    "accessory_2": {
      "text": "Subject fine jewellery to the function test. Fasten a thin white gold chain around your neck and move. If the high polish links twist or catch on a worsted wool lapel, leave it on the counter. Maintaining cool composure requires metal that sits flush and demands zero adjustment. Inspect the clasp for sharp edges. If you have to check your reflection to fix an item, it fails.",
