    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Select a small structured bag for your transit. Look for a smooth leather crossbody fitted with polished fine hardware. This item must anchor your cool composure. Rely on the physical sensation of the object rather than its appearance. Weight and friction provide the real answer. Evaluate the piece by applying the closure test. Slip the strap over your collarbone, unfasten the flap, reach inside, and snap it shut using a single hand. If the metal sticks or the leather fights your movement, drop the bag and leave it behind.",
      "sectionIntro": "Select your final utility pieces and run a rigorous physical check to ensure they perform.",
      "rankedItems": [
