    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At the office, clean geometry dictates your choices. Start with a crisp cotton poplin shirt and worsted wool trousers. Let precise seams establish boundaries. Fast movement provides your secondary check. A tight sleeve fails. A stiff collar fails. You must be able to stride across town without restriction. Introduce a solitary point of icy, cool reflection through a metallic watch. Hold yourself to a rigorous off-duty standard. Even a brief errand demands a stark navy coat and a deliberate leg crease. Never drop your silhouette for pure utility.",
