    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Your garments establish the clean geometry. Your structural fabrics ensure fast movement. Accessories step in to provide your one polished signal. Restrict yourself to one or two strong pieces per look. Before committing to any hardware, examine it from all angles. Spin the object slowly under a bare bulb and verify that the cool metal holds a rigid profile from every side. If the silhouette warps, discard it. Begin your selection with a silk band. Look for a soft glow against stark navy worsted wool. A matt finish belongs on your outer layers, not here. Secure the knot tightly and move on.",
