          "name": "Eyewear",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "thin metal frame, polished silver"
        }
      ],
      "tests": [
        "the last-look test"
      ]
    },
    "accessory_2": {
      "text": "Choose a smooth leather crossbody. Look for sharp, firm edges that maintain clean geometry when completely empty. Avoid slouchy constructions and excess pockets. Inspect the hardware closely. You need polished zips in cool silver tones that slide evenly without catching on the track. Guarantee your own sensory comfort by testing the strap flat against your collarbone under heavy load. Apply the threshold assessment before you pull the front door shut. Check your reflection and ask yourself if the strap intersects your chest awkwardly or rests securely in place. If the finish competes with your stark navy garments, take the bag off and reconsider. Trust your hands to evaluate the materials. Plating looks expensive from a distance, but the substantial weight of solid hardware reveals its true grade.",
      "sectionIntro": "Evaluate your daily carry items strictly on their structural integrity.",
      "rankedItems": [
        {
          "name": "Bags",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "smooth leather crossbody, polished zips"
        }
      ],
      "tests": [
        "the last-look test"
      ]
    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Demand strict clean geometry from your footwear. Inspect the surface for smooth leather finished with a clean gloss. Apply the same rigour to your timepiece. Select a cool steel case featuring a high polish. Gauge its quality by the solid pull in your palm. A glossy photo misrepresents craftsmanship, but the unyielding heft of solid steel answers every question. Execute the departure sweep before leaving. Remove any detail that compromises your sensory comfort or disrupts your single focal point.",
      "sectionIntro": "Audit your finishing items to ensure nothing dilutes your strict intent.",
      "rankedItems": [
        {
          "name": "Footwear",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "smooth leather, clean gloss"
