    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your signature balance relies on the friction between {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Take a piece of {texture_good_1} off the hanger. Place your left palm inside the lining and your right hand on the exterior shell. Rub them together. The layers must grip with real density. If they slip like liquid plastic, drop the item. This structural friction guarantees the garment will hold its clean geometry over a long day. Pair a dense matt weave with a cool, slick surface. Let the physical contrast anchor the outfit.",
