    "palette_narrative": {
      "text": "Keep the temperature strictly cool. Ground your base in {core_colour_1}, {core_colour_2}, {core_colour_3}, and {core_colour_4}. Deploy {accent_colour_1} or {accent_colour_2} as a single deliberate accent. Treat your relief tone as a soft note used sparingly when the eye requires a pause. Pass over hard black, harsh neon, and heavy earth brown. They will wash out your base and blur your clean geometry. Watch out for the styling pendulum. You might gather weightless sheer layers one month, then pivot entirely to stiff workwear the next. Interlock them instead. Retain an anchor from the opposite extreme in every look, without exception. Pair a fluid top with a strict trouser to maintain absolute structural control.",
