    "hardware_stones": {
      "text": "Anchor your styling with gem cuts that serve as your one hot accent. Seek absolute clarity and bold colour in {stone_1} or {stone_2}. Test the stone by letting it rest in your bare palm. A vibrant facet cuts through the room, but heavy physical mass proves the true value of the jewel. Refuse vintage, brushed, or tarnished settings outright. They look exhausted and destroy your clean impact. Demand a strictly polished, warm casing that throws blinding light back at the observer. The mount must secure the stone with aggressive, sharp edges.",
