    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Your base garments deliver clean impact. Structural cuts build sharp edges. Your accessories supply the one hot accent. Restrict yourself to one or two strong pieces per look. Begin with statement jewellery, specifically a high-polish yellow gold cuff. The surface must be mirror-bright and the metal distinctly warm. Subject every prospective piece to the isolation test. Place the object alone on a bare table. If it cannot command absolute visual dominance without a supporting outfit, do not buy it. Every final addition must govern its own space completely.",
