    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Lift a {metal_1} cuff or a piece set with {stone_1} from the counter and evaluate it in your palm. Judge the item strictly by its literal gravity. Avoid bright, mirror-like hardware. Reflective surfaces shatter your self-contained approach when placed near {core_colour_1}. Require matt or gently brushed finishes to ensure your jewellery integrates seamlessly. These subdued textures deliver clean impact and lock flawlessly into your warm wardrobe.",
      "sectionIntro": "Evaluate every piece of hardware using this simple tactile rule.",
      "tests": [
