    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Seek out keepsake jewellery in warm aged brass with a polished gold accent. This intentional approach to mixed patina and polish provides essential hidden depth. Fasten a full-grain leather belt with a brushed buckle to serve as your one hot accent. Before leaving, evaluate your visual grounding. Locate the heaviest, most stabilising item securing your outfit. If that grounding weight feels flimsy or visually detaches from your garments, strip it off and choose something entirely solid.",
      "sectionIntro": "Finalise your secondary elements and verify their physical weight before leaving.",
