    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let clean impact lead your work choices. Build a strict visual boundary using sharp wool twill and crisp cotton poplin. These fibres support you by enabling fast movement. A relentless schedule does not demand stiff armour. It requires polished cottons and yielding wools that let you sprint. Rely on your hands to evaluate these garments. Sight deceives you, but mass remains true. Complete the structure with one hot accent. Fix a deep bronze clip to a lapel or step into warm patent leather flats. Your clothes must work at your precise speed.",
      "sectionIntro": "Apply these strict directives to your working hours.",
      "tests": [
