      ]
    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "When you run to the chemist for paracetamol, hold your ground. Do not downgrade to sluggish jersey. Errands require smooth, yielding pieces that easily navigate the tarmac without sacrificing shape. Maintain your standard and demand clean impact + fast movement + one hot accent. Anchor a golden camel silk satin blouse with crisp cotton poplin. Add a highly polished bronze cuff. Test the outfit by stepping briskly down a corridor. Note how the fabric behaves in stride. Mirrors deceive, but physical restriction never lies. If a seam catches or drags, discard the item. Pick pieces that slice through the air while retaining a warm, lacquered exterior.",
      "sectionIntro": "Approach a standard Tuesday exactly as you would a major presentation, using identical rules of engagement.",
      "tests": [
