    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Build your base for clean impact. Secure your silhouette for fast movement. Finish the structure with one hot accent. Enforce this ratio by wearing strictly one or two strong pieces per look. Start with statement jewellery, selecting a high-polish yellow gold cuff. The metal must maintain an immaculate polished surface to cast a sharp, warm reflection. Subject every addition to the power-cut test. If the lights go out, the rigid metal resting on your wrist must still register as a deliberate anchor in the dark through solid weight alone.",
