    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, clean impact takes the lead. Construct your work uniform around precise cuts in bitter chocolate or dark mahogany. This creates a sharp silhouette that signals self-contained focus. Support this clear outline with blurred edges. Let a heavy silk crepe shirt soften the lines around your neck and wrists. Add one hot accent, placing warm gold jewellery at the collarbone. Never compromise physical ease for formal presentation. Apply the pharmacy test before leaving the house. If standing in the queue for a prescription feels like physical suffering, take the pieces off. Your clothing must never distract you from the work itself.",
