    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Running a morning errand does not require suffering in stiff fabrics. Keep your daily baseline comfortable and warm. Look for dense fibres. Reach for a dark mahogany washed silk shirt. Layer a matt boiled wool jumper over it. Add a polished brass ring. Your mundane routine always demands clean impact + blurred edges + one hot accent. Trust your physical comfort as your ultimate compass. Photographs fabricate. Gravity remains honest. Avoid flimsy synthetics entirely. Pick a sheer piece up and feel its lack of substance. Drop it back on the rail.",
