    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, clean impact takes the lead. Build this foundation using worsted wool trousers and crisp cotton poplin shirts in warm taupe or camel. These garments must perform silently. You depend on sensory comfort to sustain focus through long hours. If a waistband pinches or a sleeve twists, discard the piece. Finish the look with one hot accent. Choose a polished gold pin or a saffron silk square. Keep the overall effect entirely self-contained. Hold your clothing to a relentless standard. A Tuesday boardroom pitch demands flawless tailored precision. Do not compromise this baseline just because you work behind a desk.",
      "sectionIntro": "Approach your desk hours as a test of material discipline, not an audience for your wardrobe.",
