    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Anchor your layers in a cool foundation of {sweet_spot_keyword_1} worn beneath {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. This combination builds an immediate soft shelter around your frame. Add a sweater in {texture_good_1} to provide weight. Assess the drape over your arm. If the textile feels rigid or unnatural against your wrist, abandon it. Build a self-contained system using only fibres that absorb light and fall quietly.",
