    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In low light, prioritise touch over visual contrast. Your soft shelter leads here. A demanding evening does not require stiff construction. It requires pliant layers that endure until midnight. Choose cashmere knitwear in deep teal or brushed wool trousers in dove grey. Test the drape with your hands before dressing. A heavy silk shirt in inky navy must feel fluid against the collarbone, never restrictive. Ground the silhouette with a single matt silver ring. Dim lighting catches cool, muted metal and softens the edges. Reject harsh details. Focus purely on how the cloth responds to your physical movement.",
