    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your signature pairing balances {sweet_spot_keyword_1} with {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Achieve this by combining a muted, cool base with the dense weave of {texture_good_1}. Grip the sleeve without looking. If the textile feels harsh or stiff, abandon the garment immediately. It must yield under your pressure. This tactile check guarantees your clothes function as a soft shelter with hidden depth. A heavy layer over a fluid inner piece forces the materials to drape closely, keeping your silhouette self-contained. Trust your skin. It knows when a shape provides true security.",
