    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Anchor your waist with a wide full-grain leather belt featuring a cool, matt brushed buckle. This solid boundary grounds the drape of your soft shelter. Find hidden depth through keepsake jewellery. Select a deep stone set in oxidised silver. Assess the raw weight of the metal in your palm. If the setting feels hollow, leave it on the tray. Before stepping out, apply your exit test. Inspect your reflection and take off any item fighting for attention. Your self-contained quiet requires nothing extra, so one heavy piece of metal is entirely enough.",
      "sectionIntro": "Select your final functional bounds and personal stones.",
