    },
    "pattern_tip": {
      "text": "Evaluate {recommended_pattern_1} from a distance. Hang the garment on a door and retreat three paces. Without focusing directly on the fabric, ensure the print dissolves into pure, matt texture. If the shapes remain crisp and legible, leave the item on the rack. You require soft shelter. The right piece will settle into a muted, cool wash of {core_colour_1} from afar, reserving its hidden depth for your own private inspection. Run your fingers over the threads to confirm the physical reality of the weave. If the visual quietness matches the tactile density, keep it.",
      "sectionIntro": "Use this distance test to verify that your chosen prints remain private and illegible.",
      "tests": [
