    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Anchor your frame with a small structured bag. Choose a kid suede top-handle with fine matt hardware. Inspect the metal carefully to ensure it keeps the overall temperature strictly cool. Let the dense suede provide soft shelter for your daily carry. Hold the handle and gauge its physical weight. Before you step out, assess the bag in motion. Pivot completely around in front of a full-length glass to examine the piece from all angles. If the rigid geometry fights the balance of your silhouette, find another option.",
      "sectionIntro": "Finish your silhouette with a single structural anchor.",
      "rankedItems": [
