    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Establish your baseline using soft shelter. Add layers crafted from honest fabric. Finalise the outfit by selecting one sentimental keepsake. Keep your additions strictly limited to one or two functional pieces per look. Apply the handling test to every potential watch. Turn the object slowly over in your bare hands. If the metal feels dense, cool, and solid, trust it. Physical heft rarely lies. Begin with a brushed steel case attached to a leather or steel strap. Demand a strictly matt brushed surface across the hardware.",
