      "text": "Pick a medium width strip of vegetable-tanned leather to anchor your waist. Look for a cool, matt brushed buckle. The steel hardware must mirror your icy grey choices. Treat this strap as a firm boundary for your honest fabric. Apply the context test. Picture shifting this single belt between worsted wool and technical nylon trousers. If the item demands a specific garment to function, put it back. Trust your hands when examining the hide. True leather warms to the touch and bends without fighting your grip.",
