    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Evaluate your bags purely by their utility and construction. Select a canvas and leather tote or a structured briefcase. Inspect the hardware closely. The metal elements demand a muted, matt surface to uphold your cool dominant strategy. Your carrying pieces must rely on honest fabric just as your coats and trousers provide soft shelter. Put any questionable item through a strict deprivation trial. Hide the bag in a dark cupboard for two weeks. If you do not instinctively search for it during that time, permanently remove it from your possession.",
