    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Drape your {texture_good_1} over your wrist in a shadowy room. Watch how the surface absorbs ambient warmth rather than reflecting it. This optical property signals true quality. Build your outfits at the friction point between {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2} to establish hidden depth. Trust your hands when pairing these pieces. Heavy fibres drop beautifully and ground your silhouette. Look for a dense, matt weave that anchors the cloth. Let gravity prove the value of the textile.",
