    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, enduring structure leads your choices. Let the strict shoulder of a warm camel hair blazer with matt gold buttons provide a firm boundary. Subtle depth and a living element support this framework. Layer a matt silk blouse under that heavy jacket to build complexity. Depend on your bodily instinct. Mirrors deceive you. The sheer weight of a garment never lies. Grasp the fabric. Look for thick full-grain leather bags in rich toffee that stand upright on their own, and avoid flimsy materials that collapse. A Saturday morning run to an outdoor food stall is still a distinct occasion. If your tailored trousers feel too precious to wear while selecting apples, leave them on the hanger.",
