    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Accessories complete your formula. They ground your enduring structure and pull forward your hidden depth, allowing you to introduce exactly one living texture. Restrict yourself to one or two strong pieces per look. Start with handbags. Demand thick full-grain leather and brushed matt hardware that radiates a warm, muted glow. Apply the heirloom test before acquiring anything new. Run your fingers over the seams and weigh the metal components in your palm. Ask yourself if a future generation will eagerly inherit this exact piece decades from now. If the construction feels hollow or the surface gleams harshly, leave it behind. True quality reveals itself in density and lasting resilience.",
