    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At the desk, let light movement take the lead. Build your daily uniform around a crisp cotton poplin shirt that shifts easily as you draft. The other elements must support this ease. Ground the outfit with a warm camel worsted wool trouser to provide a steady, reliable foundation. Introduce one living texture through a fine ribbed merino knit to soften the sharp edges. Rely on a dual-register metal watch with a strictly matt finish to bridge the gap between formal and practical. Stepping away from the office for a lunch meeting does not justify abandoning your structure. Avoid downgrading your outerwear just to grab food. Keep your tailored layers intact.",
      "sectionIntro": "Set the terms of your daily professional environment.",
      "tests": [
