    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "A quick walk for a morning espresso demands the same warm, matt finish as a scheduled meeting. Treat a mundane trip to the shops exactly as you would a formal appointment. Anchor your day with the formula of enduring structure + light movement + one living texture. Build this foundation using a crisp cotton poplin shirt layered under a warm taupe worsted wool jacket. Test your pieces by how they function in transit. Pull a technical nylon tote over your shoulder and step into flat camel leather boots. If the combination feels restrictive on the pavement, discard it.",
      "sectionIntro": "Treat ordinary tasks as a strict testing ground for your garments.",
