    },
    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Anchor your enduring structure with {metal_1} that possesses real gravity. Weigh the piece strictly by its feeling in your hand. Flimsy construction cannot anchor an outfit. High-shine, polished chrome cuts a sharp, distracting glare against soft, warm colours. Require matt and brushed textures to keep the look cohesive. If a {stone_1} or a metal clasp feels hollow, leave it on the shelf.",
      "sectionIntro": "Evaluate every piece of hardware for physical density before you commit to wearing it.",
      "tests": [
