      ]
    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your ideal friction pairs {sweet_spot_keyword_1} with {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Put every {texture_good_1} piece through the wrist test. Rub the weave over your radial pulse point. The material must yield to fast movement while retaining a heavy, warm drape. Look for a matt surface. Avoid anything stiff. Pick it up and let it drop. If the cloth falls without life, leave it on the rail. Assess the tension. Cloth must bend when you breathe.",
