      "text": "At the desk, fast movement leads. Anchor this velocity with heavy camel outerwear and a muted silk lining that stays hidden close to your skin. Build from a warm toffee base. Avoid flimsy trousers that collapse by midday. Pick up the blazer and test the resistance of the lapel. Rely on the tension to secure a firm edge. A brisk walk outside does not demand dropping your silhouette. Keep the sharp shoulder intact even when crossing the street. Look for matt brushed wool that refuses to crease under pressure. Finish the cuff with heavy gold to bring solid gravity to the wrist.",
