    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Your wardrobe relies on enduring structure and sensory comfort. Require your accessories to supply exactly one living texture. Anchor your daily choices by wearing only one or two strong pieces per look. Start your selection with handbags. Look for warm full-grain leather secured with brushed matt hardware. Trust your hands to evaluate these objects. Examine the bag for generational stamina. Pick it up by its strap and feel the density of the hide. If the stitching and hardware would not survive decades of rigorous use, leave it on the shelf. The visual appearance deceives, but the physical construction remains absolute.",
