    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "A Tuesday morning desk shift demands the exact same standard of dress as a board presentation. At work, mobile layers must lead your approach. Support them with crisp poplin shirts and a sudden contrast in mixed metals. Pick up a worsted wool blazer and squeeze the sleeve. Grip the fabric tightly. Your tactile sense reveals whether a garment will adapt to a busy schedule or restrict you. Rely on a cool palette of stark navy and icy grey to maintain focus.",
