    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Smash {sweet_spot_keyword_1} directly against {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. This combination enforces crisp separation. Check every piece of cloth before you accept it. Stretch the yardage hard between your fists and release it. Listen for a sharp crack in the air. If the fabric sags or collapses, walk away. Your grip always detects when a weave holds structural tension. Introduce {texture_good_1} to keep the overall temperature cool.",
      "sectionIntro": "Establish your baseline material pairing.",
