      ]
    },
    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In intimate evening settings, crisp separation leads your approach. When shadows obscure colour, structural boundaries do the necessary work. Pick up a deep teal silk blouse and examine its drape. Evaluate the garment solely by its friction against your fingertips. Physical substance outranks any reflection. Combine silk with dove grey brushed wool trousers to establish clear transitions felt in close proximity. Dropping an inky navy cashmere wrap at the dry cleaner does not suspend your baseline standards. Demand garments that perform exceptionally well up close. A cashmere knit must feel substantial and cool under your grip. Finish with muted white gold.",
      "sectionIntro": "Master the physical realities of low-light dressing by commanding what cannot be clearly seen.",
      "tests": [
