    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "A quick dash to the post office does not excuse a drop in calibre. Maintain crisp separation + hidden depth + one clever contrast across all daylight hours. Pair a dove grey brushed wool trouser with an inky navy cotton overshirt. Let your fingers dictate the purchase. Ignore the showroom presentation. Gauge quality strictly by the dense drag of heavy cashmere. Keep the palette resolutely cool. Fasten a dull silver cuff to break the muted surface. Grasp the fabric blindly before putting it on your body.",
      "sectionIntro": "Treat your daily routine with absolute precision.",
      "tests": [
