      ]
    },
    "hardware_metals": {
      "text": "Your hardware strategy demands cool metals. Anchor your wardrobe with {metal_1}, {metal_2}, and {metal_3}. A highly reflective finish throws a sharp distraction across subdued fabrics. Prevent this clash by sourcing brushed and matt textures. They lock the look together and ensure crisp separation against the cloth. Never judge a buckle or watch by its appearance alone. Lift the piece and judge its heft in your palm. True mass reveals what a polished surface attempts to hide. A solid {metal_2} zip pull provides hidden depth. Reject anything that feels hollow. Avoid {excluded_finish} surfaces entirely.",
