    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your signature pairing merges {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Make this combination your baseline. When evaluating a new piece of {texture_good_1}, snap your wrist outward in a quick arc. The cuff must travel with you and return instantly to its original shape. This sharp motion proves you have secured light movement rather than rigid bulk. Heavy materials drag on your joints. Weak cloth will simply crumple. Insist on a cool surface that responds to your physical input.",
      "sectionIntro": "Anchor your wardrobe in materials that obey your physical commands.",
