    "pattern_narrative": {
      "text": "Tailored garments demand geometric precision. Anchor structured jackets with {recommended_pattern_1} to establish crisp separation. Your fluid shirts carry {recommended_pattern_2} or {recommended_pattern_3} to facilitate light movement. Select patterns with an adaptive contrast that shifts easily between formal and relaxed environments. Keep the underlying tones strictly cool. Apply a rapid visual check before adding a new print to your collection. Step back and scan the garment from a distance. It must register as a pleasing overall wash of texture, never a shouting motif that demands immediate attention. Pass over extreme graphics. Leave {avoid_pattern_1} and {avoid_pattern_2} on the hanger. If a graphic overpowers the textile itself, put the item down.",
