    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Anchor your cool palette with a small structured bag. Reach for a top-handle silhouette in kid suede or smooth leather. Inspect the clasps and rings. Choose fine mixed hardware that merges gold and silver tones without heavy ornamentation. This compact shape delivers crisp separation when set against soft fabrics. Finish with a focal scan. Evaluate your entire outfit for competing messages. If the brass clasp on your top-handle shouts over a silver pendant, the system fails. Identify the single strongest element. Remove any secondary item that fights it for attention.",
      "sectionIntro": "Select your final accessory to enforce structure and apply your exit checks.",
      "rankedItems": [
