    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Press your bare thumb into the cloth. If the weave fights your grip or slides with a high-friction glide between your fingers, leave it behind. Rely strictly on tactile feedback. Ignore the visual drape on the hanger. Gauge the density instead. Your most effective pairings live entirely in the space between {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Combine them using {texture_good_1} to establish a cool, matt foundation. This approach guarantees crisp separation between pieces while keeping your finish muted.",
      "sectionIntro": "Master your fabric combinations by testing them in your hands.",
