    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Crisp separation dictates your office strategy. Reviewing briefs on a rushed morning never justifies a careless silhouette. Establish firm boundaries using structured dove grey wool trousers or an inky navy jacket. Feel the weave of the cloth. Rely on this tactile feedback to ensure the fabric holds its cut. Soften these rigid margins by layering matt silk underneath. Finish the look by introducing a single unexpected detail at the collar, supplying one clever contrast. Look for a cool palette that maintains visual discipline. Avoid garments that slump or lose their tailoring.",
