    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In close quarters and dim lighting, crisp separation takes the lead. Shadows swallow subtle details. Keep your boundaries sharp. Pair a deep teal silk shirt with dove grey brushed wool trousers. Wear matt platinum rings rather than reflective metals to maintain a strictly cool tone. Drop any items that feel flimsy. Rely on the heavy drape of good fabric. This discipline applies to casual hours too. Sifting through produce on a brisk market morning offers no excuse to let standards slip. Keep your hem lengths exact and your shoulders defined. Wear an inky navy cashmere jumper and enforce those precise lines.",
