    "pattern_tip": {
      "text": "Test {recommended_pattern_1} under motion. Walk past a mirror without stopping. If the motif smears into an indistinguishable block of noise, leave the garment on the rack. You require absolute visual clarity to anchor your cool palette. A successful print registers instantly. Rely on your immediate physical reaction to judge legibility. When the design passes this passing check, run your fingers over the weave to verify its sensory comfort. Maintain crisp separation across every layer by refusing prints that confuse the eye.",
      "sectionIntro": "Apply the blink test to every pattern.",
