  "venus_leo__moon_aquarius__air_dominant": {
    "coreFormula": "dark drama + mobile layers + one molten flash",
    "closing": "Rely entirely on your hands to gauge the structural truth of every garment, letting physical density anchor your dark drama + mobile layers + one molten flash.",
    "style_core": {
      "text": "Trust your physical instinct for kinetic potential. Build your collection with slow deliberation, and deploy it fast. When you lift a garment from the rail, test its weight against your need for constant movement. Your core formula is dark drama + mobile layers + one molten flash. Picture a heavy, sweeping dark overcoat worn over a fine, fluid knit, anchored by a single, highly polished piece of warm jewellery resting against the collarbone.\n\nApply the treaty test to every new acquisition. Look at the garment and ask if it brokers peace between your shifting environments. A truly adaptable wardrobe connects you to your community. Every successful item bridges your morning obligations and your evening allies without forcing a change of character. If a piece demands you abandon your mobility to serve its rigid structure, drop it immediately. Seek a polished finish that communicates clearly to everyone you encounter. Trust this physical instinct as your ultimate compass. Looks lie. Weight doesn't.",
      "sectionIntro": "Memorise this blueprint before you inspect another garment.",
      "tests": [
