    "pattern_narrative": {
      "text": "Enforce a strict high-contrast graphic rule. Pattern is a tool to engineer dark drama. Tailored structures build their architecture on {recommended_pattern_1}. Fluid silks take their power from the striking scale of {recommended_pattern_2}. Require sharp edges in every motif you select. Evaluate every piece at a distance. If the visual tension dissolves into a blurry wash from across the room, leave it on the rail. The geometry must stand stark and legible from an intersection away. Pass over {avoid_pattern_1} and {avoid_pattern_2} entirely. They dilute your strict boundaries. Keep the palette warm and the final finish polished. Pick up the garment. Rely on the physical resistance in your fingers before evaluating the design. Heft provides the final confirmation.",
