    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Find the exact intersection of {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Your true baseline lives where thick, structured layers yield to pure softness. Combine a heavy {texture_good_1} outer shell with a warm, pliant base layer. Assess any new material by crushing the weave in your fist. You need fabrics that feel substantial in the palm but fold instantly when you bend your elbow. Lock these tactile extremes together to anchor your style.",
