    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let quiet grandeur take the lead at your desk. Build the entire foundation from heavy camel brushed wool and rich toffee silk. Manage the yielding materials by giving them strict structural jobs. Choose a full-grain leather briefcase that stands upright on the floor. Support this base with a solitary flash of warm metal. Fasten a heavy matt gold cuff directly over your sleeve. Taking the dog out at dawn demands the exact same standard of heavy camel brushed wool as a formal board presentation. Put on the substantial garments before you review a single document. If a blazer feels hollow to the touch, drop it immediately.",
