    "hardware_metals": {
      "text": "Your hardware follows a warm-dominant strategy. Anchor your foundation in {metal_1} and {metal_2}. These tones support your warm palette. Mix your finishes freely across your jewellery and structural zips. You can layer brushed {metal_3} directly beside a glossy clasp, provided you bypass {excluded_finish}. Lift every chain and buckle before you purchase. Assess the true quality through the dead weight of the item. Guard against icy reflections that slice through your signature softness. Highly polished cool hardware turns glaring against muted fabrics. Stick to matt and brushed textures to keep your wardrobe cohesive.",
