    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your ideal combination lives exactly where {sweet_spot_keyword_1} strikes {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Build dark drama through sharp, warm contrasts. Test a {texture_good_1} garment by sliding a fingertip along the lapel. You want a slick, immediate drop. If the material slows your movement, put the item back. You need crisp materials that reflect light in a hard, brilliant glare. Let the lack of friction guide your choices. Mirrors deceive, but surface tension tells the truth.",
      "sectionIntro": "Master this physical combination to build outfits that feel exactly right before you even look in a mirror.",
