      "tests": [
        "the keepsake test"
      ]
    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Ground your warm palette with belts cut from full-grain leather, closing them with a simple brushed buckle. Anchor this quiet grandeur with solid jewellery that balances mixed patina and polish. Seek out aged brass with a polished gold accent to provide depth. Finally, scrutinise the weight of these objects in your hands. Trust your tactile senses completely. Gloss misleads, but physical substance leaves no doubt. If a brass pendant or leather strap feels flimsy, synthetic, or freshly stamped from a modern production line, remove it immediately. The items you keep on your body must feel like heavy relics inherited from a hidden private vault.",
      "sectionIntro": "Evaluate your final layers of leather and metal before stepping out.",
      "rankedItems": [
        {
          "name": "Keepsake jewellery",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "aged brass with a polished gold accent, mixed patina and polish"
        },
