    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, hidden depth leads your strategy. Anchor yourself in a stark navy worsted wool suit or an icy grey fine ribbed merino sweater. Let balanced proportions act as your supporting framework through sharp trouser creases and exact cuffs. Finish the look with one refined touch. A cool steel watch or a mixed matt silver and gold ring does the work. Rely on your bones and skin to judge a fit. The mirror lies. Fabric tension tells the truth. Pick up a crisp cotton poplin shirt and reach forward. If the seams dig into your shoulders, discard it. A midday dash for espresso does not require stripping off your blazer. Keep the jacket on.",
