    "hardware_metals": {
      "text": "Your strategy relies on cool dominance. Anchor your jewellery and structural elements in {metal_1}, {metal_2}, and {metal_3}. Highly reflective silver strikes a jarring, distracting note against subdued textiles. Correct this disconnect by demanding matt and brushed textures, entirely rejecting {excluded_finish} finishes. This restraint ensures your metals integrate seamlessly into the overarching softness of your wardrobe. Always lift a piece to gauge its density before acquiring it. Check the gravity of the object. A solid, heavy mass confirms its worth.",
