    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Test the physical presence of an item before evaluating its design. Weigh the {metal_1} in your palm. If it feels hollow, put it down. Substantial heft anchors the softness of your garments. Maintain your balanced proportions by inspecting the surface treatment. Gleaming metal creates a harsh glare against cool, muted colours. Fix this failure by demanding brushed or matt textures. A dense, subdued finish integrates securely into your aesthetic, providing that final one refined touch.",
