      ]
    },
    "pattern_tip": {
      "text": "Subject any {recommended_pattern_1} to the twilight test. View the garment in natural dusk lighting. Squint at the fabric and monitor your immediate physical response. The motif must absorb into the underlying weave and blur at its boundaries. Look for an effect where the contrast entirely drops away. If the shapes detach from the background as the light fades, leave the item on the rail. You require strict balanced proportions, not competing graphics. A print that demands attention breaks that discipline. Demand absolute visual softness from every motif. The design must remain strictly cool and merge quietly into the twilight.",
