      "text": "Grasp the fabric with both fists and pull outward. If it stays rigid, drop it immediately. Your optimal drape requires {sweet_spot_keyword_1} paired with {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Look for the yielding quality of {texture_good_1}. This specific combination ensures light movement across your frame. Keep the visual impression cool and entirely matt. Do not trust the mirror. Feel the tension in the weave. Rely on this tactile check to filter out stiff or heavy alternatives.",
