    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your ideal tension lies between {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Blend these extremes to maintain balanced proportions across your silhouette. Pick up a piece of {texture_good_1} and test its drape. Put the item on and bend your arms fully. If the weave digs into your skin or restricts your shape at the elbows, drop it. You require pieces that offer tactile ease without losing their cool structure. Combine a matt finish with a slight sheen to build depth. Run your fingers over every internal seam before purchasing. Your fingertips verify sensory comfort long before the fitting room glass confirms the fit.",
