    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, let one refined touch lead your daily choices. Establish a sharp baseline using crisp cotton poplin and stark navy worsted wool. Rely on your immediate physical reaction to a material. If the weave feels insubstantial, discard the item. Once you secure a grounding layer, introduce a single piece of matt white gold or a sleek steel watch to finish the look. Avoid piling on details. A rushed morning walk for espresso in freezing rain requires the exact same level of sensory comfort as a board meeting. Do not save premium icy grey knits for major presentations. Pick up a fine ribbed merino sweater and assess the gauge to guarantee balanced proportions. Ensure every item maintains a cool temperature and adapts to your shifting environments.",
