    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let balanced proportions lead your choices at the office. Your clothing must frame your shoulders precisely. Sensory comfort provides the foundation underneath. Reach for heavy silk crepe trousers or a boiled wool jacket. Both must feel completely weightless against the skin. Let one refined touch establish the final boundary. A cool, matt platinum ring brings sharp focus to a dove grey shirt. Apply your own standard to every environment. Buying lightbulbs on a Saturday morning requires the exact same crisp fit as a Monday board presentation. Trust the cut of the cloth over the expectations of the room.",
      "sectionIntro": "Establish your professional boundaries by setting strict physical standards for your working environment.",
      "tests": [
