  "venus_pisces__moon_aries__water_dominant": {
    "coreFormula": "weightless layers + sharp edges + one pearl of light",
    "closing": "Trust the physical weight of the fabric to map your absolute boundaries, filtering every choice through weightless layers + sharp edges + one pearl of light.",
    "style_core": {
      "text": "Ground your choices in the sensation of absolute silence. Trust this physical instinct as your ultimate compass. When you handle a garment, test it for structural precision without bulk. The material should drape clean and stand slightly away from the body. Your system relies on a strict equation. Anchor every look in weightless layers + sharp edges + one pearl of light. Picture a translucent, matt underlayer beneath a tailored jacket with a razor-sharp lapel, finished with a single, cool point of illumination at the throat. The architecture builds a boundary.\n\nConstruct your collection with deliberate slowness. Curate the pieces meticulously, but deploy them fast. Your wardrobe must function as a strictly self-contained system where every item links flawlessly to the next. Before you acquire anything new, apply the breath test. Put the garment on and monitor your respiration. If the cut restricts your ribs or the fabric drag forces a shallow inhale, take it off immediately. The structure must permit a deep, steady rhythm. If a piece requires constant physical management or narrows your lung capacity, leave it behind.",
      "sectionIntro": "Treat this foundation as your structural blueprint, an unyielding set of rules for constructing a wardrobe that operates on pure precision.",
      "tests": [
        "the breath test"
      ]
    },
