    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, let one pearl of light lead your approach. Your fluid drapes and unrestrictive silhouettes support this focal point by building a muted, cool colour foundation. A high-stakes board meeting does not require surrendering your softness. Leave stiff, starchy cotton on the rack. Touch proves the quality. Pair an inky navy silk blouse with brushed dove grey wool trousers. Ground the uniform with a single matt silver cuff at the wrist. This quiet metal finish anchors the eye, resting perfectly against a deep teal cashmere wrap.",
      "sectionIntro": "Apply your core aesthetic principles to an office environment with deliberate precision.",
