    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "You have established a base of weightless layers and added mobile layers. Now you must set one pearl of light. Restrict your finish to one or two strong pieces per look. Start with handbags crafted from full-grain leather. Seek out structured shapes finished with brushed matt hardware. Before purchasing, apply the keepsake test. Pick the bag up and ask if you would confidently hand it down to the next generation. If the item feels temporary, leave it on the shelf. The solid heft of a cool metal clasp provides all the confirmation you need.",
