    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Hold the cloth to your lips and blow through the weave. If you feel the moving air on the back of your hand, buy it. Look for the precise intersection of {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Build your wardrobe around these weightless layers. Keep the finish entirely matt and the palette cool. Avoid anything that traps heat or feels rigid. Your materials must drape silently. Demand total freedom of movement from every item you put on.",
