    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let weightless layers take the primary role at your desk. Build the foundation with a dove grey cashmere knit beneath an inky navy brushed wool blazer. The silhouette stays private and contained. Let yielding texture support the rigid tailoring through a fluid silk shirt. Complete the uniform with a single bright accent, like a matt silver watch sitting flat on the wrist. Maintain this discipline relentlessly. A sprint to the corner café for an espresso does not excuse a lapse in structure. Keep the lines clean and the palette cool. Avoid shifting into shapeless knits when the office chills. Trust dense fibres to retain your form from the morning commute until you log off.",
