    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Accessories furnish the one pearl of light that finalises your silhouette. Secure your weightless layers and essential softness, then stop. Commit to one or two strong pieces per look. Put every choice through the hearth test. A successful piece holds its presence like a solitary spark resting on cool ash. If it casts a wide beam, abandon it. Handbags must observe the same strict boundaries. Demand full-grain leather or thick suede. Inspect the bag to ensure all hardware remains matt and brushed. Pick it up and evaluate the construction. Feel the dense grain of the hide and the heavy drag of the metal. These tactile metrics give you the only honest assessment of quality.",
