    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At the desk, maintain weightless layers + athletic space + one pearl of light. The distance between cloth and skin gives you room to operate, while breathable fabrics regulate the cool office air. Support this volume with a single point of brightness at the collar to direct the eye. Do not reserve your highest quality items for important calendar blocks. Leading a strategy meeting demands the same standard as drafting emails alone. Pick up a heavy silk crepe blouse. If it feels too precious for an ordinary afternoon, leave it on the hanger. Test the drape physically. Glass deceives, but true cloth tells the truth.",
      "sectionIntro": "Treat your work environment as a rigorous testing ground for your personal standard.",
