    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In dim lighting, maintain weightless layers + athletic space + one pearl of light. Reach for a single matt silver ring or a pale moonstone pendant to cut through the shadows. Anchor this brightness with cool, muted shades like dove grey or deep teal. Close your eyes and handle the garments before you dress. Since reflections lie, the pure downward drag of a woven textile proves its worth. Rely entirely on this blind touch test. Taking a midnight walk demands the exact same standard of dress as sitting down to a private dinner. Wrap cloud-soft lambswool over your shoulders. Discard any piece that feels rigid, letting pure gravity dictate your shape.",
