    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Treat a mundane grocery run with the identical baseline as a formal gathering. Do not suspend your rules for the post office queue. Select dove grey boiled wool and fine cashmere. Assess the give of the sleeve. If the garment restricts your arms, leave it behind. Maintain weightless layers + athletic space + one pearl of light at all times. Anchor a muted deep teal shirt with a single platinum chain. Evaluate the textile blindly. If the weave feels unyielding, reject it. Cool tones require a matt finish to function properly. Dress for the routine errand using your highest criteria.",
