    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, weightless layers lead the equation. They build a private, silent enclosure of brushed wool or fine cashmere to guard against the room. Support this structure with a hushed base of deep teal and inky navy. Keep the silhouette close and strict. Finish the system with one pearl of light, a single white gold cuff or a platinum watch, to draw focus without shouting. Test the integrity of your uniform whenever you leave the desk. Stepping out for a coffee does not require stripping away your private, cool climate. Keep the dove grey coat buttoned.",
