    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "Your quiet undercurrent must lead in low light. In a dim room, vision fails and texture takes control. Reach for deep teal silk or dove grey cashmere. Trust your hands. Let the fabric slip through your fingers to confirm its muted density. Transitioning to a private dinner demands the identical exacting standards. Bring the exact same cool atmosphere into the evening. Combine a full-grain leather jacket with an inky navy knit. Keep all metals cool and matt. Reject stiff synthetic blends. Let the self-contained drape of brushed tweed set the boundary.",
