    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Your baseline does not evaporate when you step out to fetch paracetamol from the chemist. Errands demand the same rigid framework as formal appointments. Maintain your strict logic. Rely on the immediate sensation of the cloth against your collarbone to make your morning decisions. Apply weightless layers + quiet undercurrent + one pearl of light as your absolute constant. Slip a deep teal cashmere jumper over dove grey silk. Shrug on a brushed wool coat in inky navy. Anchor the wrist with a single matt silver cuff. Avoid reaching for unconsidered jersey staples merely to run down the street. Preserve a cool, muted barrier that functions entirely for you.",
