    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Combine {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2} to build a self-contained foundation. Let your skin be the final judge. Pick up a {texture_good_1} jacket and examine it away from harsh store lighting. If the surface drinks the ambient glow and holds a cool, matt depth, keep it. Avoid any thread that flashes or reflects. You require structured cloth that folds seamlessly into weightless layers. Grip the lapel to verify the true quality and substance of the woven seam.",
