      "text": "In dim, private environments, allow one pearl of light to lead your approach. Strip away excess metal. Let a solitary cool moonstone or a brushed silver watch dial catch the ambient shadows. Read the drape of your evening garments against your collarbone. If a seam pinches or restricts your movement in the slightest, discard the piece. Your muscles recognise poor construction before your eyes register it. Choose matt inky navy cashmere that absorbs the background and rely solely on that singular illuminated focal point. Let deep teal textiles recede gracefully. Self-contained style operates best when you refuse to over-accessorise. Demand subtle woven textures and crisp hemlines to complete the look.",
