      "text": "Never suspend your standards for mundane errands. Demand absolute consistency from your wardrobe every day of the week. Keep your approach strictly anchored to weightless layers + sensory comfort + one pearl of light. Pull on a dove grey cashmere jumper to buy groceries. Fasten a cool silver watch to your wrist for a simple walk. Let these muted garments construct a quiet, self-contained barrier between you and the outside world. Discard any item that shifts out of place while you are in motion.",
      "sectionIntro": "Maintain absolute strictness in your daily dressing routines.",
