    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let light movement dictate your working garments. Establish a fluid foundation with fine ribbed merino. Support this leading element by washing the rest of the shape in broad, warm hues using camel worsted wool. Complete the silhouette by deploying one theatrical finish, perhaps a heavy mixed metal cuff at the wrist. Keep these parameters strict on administrative days. Taking your crisp cotton poplin to the dry cleaner does not excuse a lapse in standards. Avoid defaulting to unstructured grey jersey.",
      "sectionIntro": "Treat your professional garments as a strict physical discipline, not a default uniform.",
      "tests": [
