  "venus_sagittarius__moon_leo__fire_dominant": {
    "coreFormula": "expansive colour + athletic space + one theatrical finish",
    "closing": "Your style guide is a map of your own instincts, built on expansive colour + athletic space + one theatrical finish.",
    "style_core": {
      "text": "Trust the sensory compass of warm, kinetic stretch. A garment must accommodate immediate, sweeping physical movement while catching the light with a high-shine, polished surface. Build your outfits on the exact equation of expansive colour + athletic space + one theatrical finish. Picture a highly saturated, oversized technical windbreaker layered over a close-fitting performance base, grounded by a pair of heavily glossed, architectural boots. The volume gives you the physical room to operate. The high-gloss finish provides the staging.\n\nLet your daily dressing tempo run on instinct. Assemble your pieces rapidly based on immediate momentum, drifting by mood rather than strict planning. When evaluating a new garment, apply the hesitation test. If you pick up a voluminous shell and pause to question if the shape is too loud for your community, put it down. That physical stall means the item lacks the open conviction your wardrobe demands. Trust your hands as your ultimate compass. Looks lie. That split-second physical doubt tells the entire truth.",
      "sectionIntro": "Memorise these base mechanics before you evaluate another garment.",
      "tests": [
        "the hesitation test"
      ]
    },
    "textures_good": {
      "text": "Build your wardrobe on materials that carry expansive colour and protect your athletic space while delivering one theatrical finish. Look for {texture_good_1} when buying sharp shirting that holds a crisp fold, and demand {texture_good_2} for knife-edge tailoring that refuses to wilt. Elevate these garments with warm {texture_good_3} in your footwear to reflect maximum light. Use {texture_good_4} for linings that gleam when you move. Verify the polish directly on the shop floor. Perform the friction test. Run your palm swiftly down the sleeve and seek the immediate slip. If the surface drags, drop the garment. Focus exclusively on this ranked list.",
