    "textures_bad": {
      "text": "Test for resistance immediately. {texture_bad_1} fails this check instantly. It bites back, gripping the skin and collapsing your athletic space. Drop it. Reject {texture_bad_2} just as quickly. It feels like warm dust against the neck and swallows light rather than throwing a polished gleam. Avoid {texture_bad_3} entirely. It catches on your mixed metals and pulls. When you navigate a dense crowd, you require materials that slip and shine. Dead, dragging fabrics only tie you down.",
      "sectionIntro": "Identify and eliminate materials that drag against your skin.",
      "tests": [
