    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Aim for the precise intersection of {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Pick up a piece of {texture_good_1} and assess the surface tension. Brush your knuckles rapidly across the jacket arm. You need a completely frictionless finish to construct an athletic space that genuinely moves with you. Pair this slick outer layer with warm, mixed hardware to anchor the shape. Combine these components without ever sacrificing that fast, clean slide. Trust this physical feedback. A heavy drag confirms a failing garment.",
      "sectionIntro": "Master the physical weight of your clothes to dictate your aesthetic.",
      "tests": [
        "the friction test (run your hand swiftly down the sleeve; seek the slip)"
      ]
    },
    "palette_narrative": {
      "text": "Anchor the foundation in {core_colour_1} and {core_colour_2}. Substitute stark white with {core_colour_3} and bridge gaps using {core_colour_4}. Treat this palette as a warm baseline. Bring expansive colour into the equation using {accent_colour_1} and {accent_colour_2}. Deploy the relief tone as a soft note used sparingly to give the eye a brief rest. Bypass muddy pastel, icy grey, and dusty sage. Test every item before buying. Watch out for the fade trap. When pale or lifeless pieces drain your natural vitality, fix the error fast. Rescue the look instantly by placing a saturated focal point at the collarbone or grounding the outfit with a brilliant shoe. Keep the shape crisp to carve out an athletic space within the room.",
      "sectionIntro": "Build your palette like a strict toolkit, selecting tones that construct shape and project vitality.",
