        "the wrist-flick test"
      ]
    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Hold {sweet_spot_keyword_1} next to {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Shake the textile vigorously. The material must drop back into its original drape in a single beat. Build your outfits around this rapid recovery. It guarantees cool composure as you navigate your day and engage your community. Incorporate {texture_good_1} to keep the combination warm and adaptable. Let the materials do the heavy lifting. Rely on how a garment falls from your own arm rather than how it looks on a static display.",
      "sectionIntro": "Combine your most reliable textiles by testing how they behave on your own body.",
