    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let cool composure lead your working hours. Support this foundation with broad stretches of a warm hue, layering a camel fine ribbed merino polo under a warm taupe technical nylon shell. Establish a theatrical accent with a solid brass ring. Evaluate your choices before leaving the house. Stand still and visualise the queue at the pharmacy. If your worsted wool trousers pinch or drag while you wait for a prescription, discard the item. Never accept physical discomfort for the sake of an office silhouette.",
