    "hardware_metals": {
      "text": "You possess total freedom to mix {metal_1}, {metal_2}, and {metal_3}. Since your palette is warm, allow these metals to mingle seamlessly across your body. A wardrobe rooted in expansive colour demands deliberate hardware choices. Stay entirely away from {excluded_finish} surfaces. High-gloss polished silver throws a harsh, distracting glare against soft muted fabrics. Restrict your jewellery and buckles strictly to matt and brushed textures to maintain a cohesive surface. Assess a metal's mass by holding it in your palm. Photographs obscure reality, but solid density cannot be faked. Base your choices on the heavy, solid drag of genuine metal.",
