    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Locate your sweet spot exactly where {sweet_spot_keyword_1} meets {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Measure {texture_good_1} by how heavily it pools from your fingers. You require materials that hold sharp edges without adding rigid bulk. Test the weave by checking its density against a stiff breeze. The air must stop dead. If a draft pushes through easily, leave the item on the rack. You need a solid barrier that keeps you warm. Look for a matt surface that stays entirely self-contained.",
      "sectionIntro": "Master the physical tests required to secure your ideal material match.",
      "tests": [
