    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Pair {sweet_spot_keyword_1} with {sweet_spot_keyword_2} to build quiet complexity. Reach for {texture_good_1} to ground the combination. Trust your hands, as your fingers comprehend the textile better than your eyes. Evaluate the breathability before purchasing. If a tightly woven synthetic stops air from passing through entirely, walk away. You require pliable materials that flow freely, allowing a close drape that holds quiet depth. Keep the finish matt. Keep the overall feel muted and warm.",
