    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let close drape lead your workday. Unseen interior depth supports this silhouette from the inside, while a solitary warm detail brings life to the surface. Form the core of your attire using a dark mahogany heavy silk crepe skirt that skims the leg. Layer a washed silk shirt underneath. Finish with a matt bronze cuff. Subject every piece to the queue test. If you cannot stand under harsh fluorescent lights waiting for cough syrup in that boiled wool jacket without tugging at the collar, put it back on the rail. Picking up medicine must never make you grit your teeth just to maintain an aesthetic.",
