    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, close drape leads the way. Anchor tailored shapes in brushed wool. Allow soft silk layers to add a gentle drift at the cuff. Support this foundation with a single warm glow of gold at the collar. Squeeze the yarn to verify its density. Apply the Ripple test to every outfit. Drape a camel coat over a rich toffee blouse to ensure the layers shift smoothly together. If any piece feels rigid, remove it immediately. Choose pliable full-grain leather for bags. Finish the look with a matt bronze watch.",
