    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Anchor your choices in the precise tension between {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Gather a piece of {texture_good_1} in your hands. It must yield instantly and pool heavily into your palms. Appearance deceives. Gravity tells the truth. If the item holds a stiff shape away from your body, leave it behind. It will never provide the necessary close drape. You require heavy, collapsing textiles that stay completely self-contained. Contrast that yielding weight against a matt, warm finish. Evaluate your fabrics strictly through their dense, settling pull.",
