    "palette_narrative": {
      "text": "Your palette runs exclusively warm. Anchor your foundation with {core_colour_1} and {core_colour_2} as base neutrals. Connect these elements using {core_colour_3} and {core_colour_4} as bridge neutrals. Introduce {accent_colour_1} or {accent_colour_2} as your single deliberate accent. Treat the relief tone strictly as a soft note used sparingly. Pass over icy electric blue, neon brights, and fleeting trend pastels without hesitation. Beware the sofa drift. Relax your garments too far and your attire devolves into loungewear. Correct this error by demanding exactly one structural boundary. Force a rolled but substantial lapel, a trouser holding a defined crease, or a firm leather bag into the ensemble to anchor your close drape.",
