    },
    "hardware_stones": {
      "text": "Anchor your warm hardware strategy with dense, opaque pieces like {stone_1} and {stone_2}. Test each stone by feeling its weight in your fingers. The physical density provides the necessary grounding for your aesthetic. You require close drape and fast movement from your garments, and your jewellery must not interrupt that flow. Do not ruin a muted finish with high-gloss polished materials. Glossy gems create a sharp glare against soft textiles. Correct this error by insisting on smooth, sanded settings that remain entirely self-contained.",
