    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Evaluate {metal_1} jewellery by testing its heft. A weighty pendant anchors your frame, providing one warm point of light that allows for fast movement without swinging wildly out of place. If the item feels hollow or insubstantial, leave it in the shop. Avoid glossy chrome completely. Highly polished silver slices sharply through muted warm colours like {core_colour_1} and distracts the eye. Choose flat matt or sanded textures to tie your clothes together and support your close drape. Rely on the grounding presence of unpolished metal to dictate your selections.",
