    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Routine errands demand the identical baseline as formal appointments. Apply your equation without exception. Every outfit must deliver close drape + sensory comfort + one warm point of light, even when you are just collecting a prescription in the rain. Build this daily structure with camel brushed wool trousers and a matt toffee silk shirt. Add a single warm gold ring. Never suspend your standard for utility. Evaluate a thick cashmere sweater by rolling the sleeve up to the elbow to check the tension. Inspect the seams on full-grain leather boots to ensure they sit cleanly at the ankle. Maintain your muted finish. Choose garments that contain your movement safely.",
      "sectionIntro": "Treat every routine errand as a strict drill to reinforce your structural baseline.",
      "tests": [
