    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Collecting a prescription from the chemist is no excuse to abandon your framework. Paying a utility bill does not require collapsing into shapeless cotton. Anchor your mornings in heavy camel brushed wool and full-grain toffee leather boots. Pick the piece up and test its density. If it sags, drop it. Trust the heavy drape of real cashmere to hold a crisp line. Keep your warm colours strict. Even on the simplest errands, demand structure + sharp edges + a touch of quiet depth without exception.",
      "sectionIntro": "Set a rigorous daily baseline and refuse to lower it for convenience.",
      "tests": [
