      ]
    },
    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In dim, intimate spaces, a touch of quiet depth takes the lead. Prioritise rich toffee silk and heavy brushed wool over pieces that reflect harsh light. Keep your palette warm and mix your metals. Pair a matt gold ring with a simple steel watch. Apply the exact same internal standard to every hour of your schedule. A late-night errand for coffee beans requires the same camel cashmere and precise tailoring as a private dinner reservation. Evaluate the drape of your clothing away from the mirror. Rely entirely on the physical weight of the garment against your skin. Appearance falls away in the dark. The heavy drop of good wool cannot be faked.",
