    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, cool composure leads your decisions. Set the baseline with a strict cut, while soft structure provides the necessary physical ease and a touch of quiet depth gives the outfit its gravity. Pick up a bitter chocolate jacket and assess the drape in your hands. A standard desk shift requires the same precise construction as a high-stakes boardroom pitch. Rely on the heavy weight of boiled wool or washed silk to dictate the silhouette. Keep the overall palette warm and the fabric finishes strictly matt. Let dark mahogany leather ground the foot. You do not dress for an audience. You select garments for the specific demands of the day, ensuring every piece pulls its weight.",
