      "text": "Dress for standing in the queue at the post office exactly as you prepare for a scheduled appointment. A trip for lightbulbs at the local hardware shop requires the exact same precise fit as a Monday morning consultation. Never let a mundane errand suspend your standards. Anchor your daily choices in your core equation. Every single day requires soft structure + cool composure + a touch of quiet depth. Layer a dark mahogany boiled wool coat over a heavy silk crepe shirt. Keep the palette temperature warm. Fasten a matt bronze belt buckle alongside a silver watch. Check the seams and shoulders before stepping outside.",
