    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "In the office, fast movement leads your choices. A quick dash to buy brass hinges requires the exact same clean drape as a Monday morning pitch. Precise tailoring holds your frame in place, while heavy silk and rich toffee cashmere provide warm grounding. Select garments that let you step swiftly from a desk to the street without adjusting a single seam. Rely on exact proportions over bright distraction. If an item demands constant fussing, discard it. A brushed camel wool jacket must sit securely on the shoulders.",
