    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Select a small structured bag for your daily carry. Look for a kid suede top-handle design. Inspect the metal closures. You need fine matt hardware in warm bronze or brushed steel to support your mixed metal strategy. Suede serves as an honest fabric here. It provides essential structure without looking rigid. Before you leave the house, conduct a practical hardware trial. Confirm the clasp releases smoothly with a single thumb. Lift the bag by the handle and assess its balance. If you must wrestle the mechanism or continuously fix your grip, abandon the piece.",
      "sectionIntro": "Secure your belongings with intentional materials and test the physical utility of every component.",
      "rankedItems": [
        {
          "name": "Small structured bag",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "kid suede top-handle, fine matt hardware"
