      "text": "Seek the friction between {sweet_spot_keyword_1} and {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. Your best outfits rely on this exact tension. Bring a {texture_good_1} item into a neutral light and inspect its surface. It should offer hidden depth rather than a flat sheen. Drape the fabric over your forearm and observe the boundaries it creates. It must hold its architecture. It must refuse to collapse into a soft heap. This structural integrity reveals the truth about garment construction. A matt finish establishes self-contained borders. Rely on this structural resistance to guide your choices.",
