    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Anchor your garments with a precise fit. Fasten them using a wide full-grain leather belt with a matt brushed buckle. Choose keepsake jewellery built around a deep stone set in oxidised aged silver or brass. Gauge the cold density of the metal. If the object feels flimsy, discard it. Isolate the strongest element before moving on. Strip away any item trying to do too much. Maintain strict self-contained boundaries. One meticulous detail is always enough.",
      "sectionIntro": "Finalise your accessories by seeking quiet density and testing your outfit for unnecessary excess.",
