    "palette_narrative": {
      "text": "Build your foundation with {core_colour_1} and {core_colour_2}. Introduce {core_colour_3} to clarify shapes and let {core_colour_4} anchor heavier tailoring. Your overall palette operates at a neutral temperature. Deploy your relief tone sparingly as a soft note to break up large solid blocks. Apply {accent_colour_1} or {accent_colour_2} strictly to deliver one meticulous detail. This approach highlights the precise fit and light movement in your styling. Pass over neon brights, hard jet black, and glitter finishes. Beware the trap of an uninspired single-shade look that leaves you feeling stagnant by lunch. Break the monotony immediately. Add a crisp {core_colour_3} poplin collar, a cool dominant structural ring, or a sharply constructed sneaker.",
