    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Your precise fit leads in the office. Secure your foundation with exactly tailored worsted wool trousers. Maintain blurred edges to ease the strictness. Layer a soft stone fine ribbed merino jumper over a crisp cotton poplin shirt, breaking the harsh lines. Introduce one meticulous detail to support the entire structure. Fasten a matt steel watch to your wrist. Evaluate the drape directly. Reflections deceive, but the heavy fall of worsted wool reveals the exact cut. Apply a rigid standard to your mornings. A demanding boardroom presentation requires the exact same quiet care as an isolated afternoon at your desk. Keep your entire palette restrained to a single neutral tone like oatmeal.",
