    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In close quarters and dim lighting, your precise fit leads. Keep your palette neutral. An oatmeal or soft stone fine ribbed merino jumper provides blurred edges, absorbing shadows quietly. Supply one meticulous detail by pairing the knit with a matt steel watch or a white gold ring. Cool metals catch low light softly. Discard any piece that demands an audience. A quiet evening reading in your study deserves the same standard. If worsted wool trousers sit right at a dining table, they work just as well lounging near a hearth. Your clothing serves you alone.",
