      ]
    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "A demanding itinerary calls for an oatmeal merino knit that flexes, rather than rigid scaffolding. Queueing at the dry cleaners for a pickup commands the exact same standard as your most formal appointments. Always return to precise fit + honest fabric + one meticulous detail. Keep the palette neutral. Anchor your morning choice in worsted wool trousers and a crisp cotton poplin shirt finished with a matt platinum collar stud. Assess the give in the cloth before putting it on. Pull the hem. Your body knows what restrictions it can tolerate. Test the resistance in the weave. If a sleeve catches when you raise your arm, discard the garment immediately.",
