    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Lift every watch, buckle, and fastening. Hold the piece in your palm to evaluate its density. A true honest fabric deserves hardware of equal substance. Brushed copper and artificially rusted elements read as clutter against a modern silhouette. They distract from a precise fit. Restrict your zips and clasps to neutral platinum, white gold, mirror chrome, or {metal_1}. A heavy matt {metal_1} closure provides exactly the structural grounding you need.",
