      ]
    },
    "hardware_metals": {
      "text": "Establish a cool metal foundation using {metal_1}, {metal_2}, and {metal_3}. Weigh the piece in your palm to assess its heft. Substantial buckles and heavy links provide necessary anchor points to a soft shelter. Keep the finishes strictly muted. High-shine {metal_1} cuts too sharply across {core_colour_1} fabrics and distracts the eye. Restrict your hardware to matt and brushed textures to lock the visual field together. Reject {excluded_finish} completely.",
      "sectionIntro": "Apply strict rules to your hardware to anchor your wardrobe.",
      "tests": [
