    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let the quiet undercurrent lead at work. Guard your energy with garments that trace a continuous, clean line. Support this primary layer with your soft shelter. Pull a dense, matt knit over your shoulders to preserve your focus and muffle ambient noise. Fasten a cool metal pendant close to the skin. Run the pharmacy line test before stepping out the door. Picture yourself standing under harsh fluorescent lights for twenty minutes waiting to collect a prescription. If a rigid collar or pinching waistband makes that wait miserable, drop the garment immediately. Sharpness never justifies restriction. Absolute ease protects your self-contained focus.",
