      "text": "Weigh the piece carefully before committing. Photographs and shop lighting deceive the eye, but gravity provides an absolute measure of quality. Handle {metal_1} or {stone_1} to confirm its integrity. A hollow, lightweight cast feels wrong immediately. Your wardrobe relies on enduring structure. High-gloss hardware disrupts this foundation. A mirror-polished surface looks jarring against a warm, muted palette. Highly reflective finishes cut aggressively into quiet fabrics and distract the eye. Choose only brushed or matt textures to integrate your hardware seamlessly.",
