      ]
    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Running errands down the high street for basic supplies does not suspend your standards. Anchor your casual garments in your required sequence of enduring structure + honest fabric + one living texture. Construct the look using foundational taupe trousers and worsted wool outerwear, just as you would for a desk shift. Layer a crisp poplin shirt under a warm fine ribbed knit. Gauge the physical heft of the garments against your skin. The weave must remain tight and the finish must stay muted and perfectly matt. Fasten a mixed steel and gold watch before you leave the house. Reject anything limp.",
      "sectionIntro": "Enforce your standard across every mundane errand and ordinary hour.",
      "tests": [
