    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, crisp separation leads your approach. Build stark boundaries between a fine ribbed merino knit and cool grey worsted wool trousers. Support this clear division with room to move. A technical nylon overcoat provides the breathable distance you need to engage comfortably with your peers. Anchor the look with an unexpected clash of details to prevent stiffness. A matt silver watch paired with a polished brass buckle does the work. Keep the entire colour palette rigorously cool. A damp weekday commute demands the exact same sharp poplin standard as a formal client presentation. Trust your hands to check the seams of every piece. If the edges feel vague or flimsy, drop the garment immediately.",
      "sectionIntro": "Calibrate your wardrobe for the working week by defining your boundaries.",
