    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "A quick trip to pick up a prescription from the local chemist requires an identical baseline of care as a scheduled community meeting. Maintain crisp separation + athletic space + one clever contrast across every ordinary task. Build these outfits on stark navy technical nylon and icy grey cotton poplin. Keep the overall temperature strictly cool. Pair a matt worsted wool trouser with a high-shine mixed metal watch to keep the visual interest active. Evaluate a garment by working in it. If a shoulder seam binds when reaching for a high shelf, discard the piece entirely.",
