    },
    "hardware_stones": {
      "text": "Demand dense, unclouded {stone_1} or highly refractive {stone_2} that cast a clean, cool light across your collarbone. Lift the piece from the counter to evaluate its heft. Appearances deceive. Grams deliver truth. Your gems must carry enough physical mass to anchor your lighter technical fabrics. Artificially distressed pieces register as visual clutter against your modern aesthetic. Leave those cloudy patinas behind. Choose strictly high-shine, mirror-polished settings to enforce crisp separation against your textiles.",
