    },
    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Weigh every piece of {metal_1} in your hand before you wear it. Visuals can be manipulated, but physical mass cannot be faked. Give your hardware a rigorous physical assessment. Oxidised edges and forced patinas register as visual debris. Demand cool, highly reflective, pristine finishes to deliver one clever contrast against your matt fabrics. Leave an athletic space around a solitary {stone_1} so the shape stands alone with crisp separation.",
