    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Anchor the cool palette with a clean leather boot. Press your thumb directly into the vamp. The calfskin must give slightly under pressure, rather than folding like cardboard. Trust this physical feedback over the brand name. Secure a fit that leaves generous athletic space across the toe box. You need crisp separation exactly where a navy worsted wool hem meets the polished hide. Let a matt zip or a scatter of mixed gold and silver eyelets deliver one clever contrast. Finally, apply the pivot assessment. Stand in your finished clothes and turn slowly on the spot. If a thick rubber sole or a gleaming zip snags your attention and pulls focus from the overall structure, take the boots off.",
      "sectionIntro": "Evaluate your foundation elements and execute a definitive exit check before you step outside.",
      "rankedItems": [
        {
          "name": "Footwear",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "clean leather boot, clean"
