    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Ground dark drama with a small structured bag. Pick a smooth leather crossbody in a deep warm colour like dark mahogany. Inspect the clasps and rings. Choose polished fine hardware that supports a dual metal approach. Review your layers before leaving. Remove the single piece doing too much work. If an extra layer interrupts the fluid light movement of your washed silk blouse, drop it immediately. Evaluate the balance practically. Rely on the raw physics of the bag.",
      "sectionIntro": "Select your final utility pieces and test the total assembly for excess.",
      "rankedItems": [
        {
          "name": "Small structured bag",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "smooth leather crossbody, polished fine hardware"
