    },
    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Always evaluate an accessory physically before committing to it. A brilliant surface catches the light, but dense mass confirms the quality. Avoid tarnished details that disrupt the clean surface of your mobile layers. Stick to the polished, cool exterior of {metal_1} or the matt weight of {stone_1}. This strict filter guarantees every piece justifies its place and maintains balanced proportions across your collection.",
      "sectionIntro": "Evaluate the true quality of your accessories through weight and touch.",
      "tests": [
