    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, cool composure leads. Establish this foundation with stark navy worsted wool and icy grey technical nylon. Support this crisp base by anchoring the silhouette with strict, clean lines. Provide the final anchor using a steel watch or a matt silk tie as your solitary focal point. Test every outfit before you step outside. If you cannot stand in the queue at the chemist for a prescription without shifting your stance or tugging at a stiff collar, leave the item on the hanger. Suffering serves no purpose here. Trust the way fine ribbed merino yields to your shoulders.",
