    "hardware_stones": {
      "text": "Evaluate {stone_1} and {stone_2} by lifting them. Images trick the brain. Weight grounds it. Assess the true value of a piece by feeling its density in your palm. High-shine silver disrupts muted cool colours with a sharp glare. Insist on matt or brushed settings to keep the visual field cohesive. When incorporating {stone_3}, ensure its surface diffuses light rather than fracturing it. Maintain exact proportions and a quiet undercurrent, allowing just a refined touch of mineral weight to anchor the garments.",
