      "text": "Anchor your garments with a medium full-grain leather belt. Select a completely matt buckle. Preserve balanced proportions by keeping this hardware firmly in your cool palette. For keepsake jewellery, source oxidised rings or cuffs cast in aged silver. Weigh these pieces in your palm. Base your judgement purely on this gravitational pull. Cold metal never lies. Finally, check for visual friction. Scan your outfit for any piece that pierces the quiet mood. If a polished pendant fractures the surface of a dove grey cashmere jumper, remove the piece.",
