    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Build your foundation by pairing {sweet_spot_keyword_1} with {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. This establishes your daily baseline. Introduce {texture_good_1} to complete the equation. Gauge every new piece by letting it fall from shoulder height. If it hits the floor with a heavy thud, put it back on the rail. You require pieces that settle gently and provide true light movement. Rely on your hands to evaluate the truth of a material. This rigorous physical assessment guarantees you construct weightless layers that never pull or restrict.",
