    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In close, low-light settings, one pearl of light leads. Dim environments obscure visual complexities. Build from icy grey crisp cotton poplin and stark navy fine ribbed merino. Ordering a midnight espresso demands the exact standard you apply to a boardroom presentation. Mix cool silver with unpolished gold to catch minimal illumination. Keep proportions strictly balanced. Combine a matt collar with a bright metallic clasp. Vision deceives in dark rooms. Mass reveals the truth. Run your hands over the material to confirm its density before putting it on.",
      "sectionIntro": "Assess intimate spaces and low-light environments.",
      "tests": [
