    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Taking the terrier out in the rain requires the exact same structural integrity as an afternoon strategy session. Grabbing a prescription from the high street chemist is no excuse to drop your standard. Keep your methodology strict. Execute weightless layers + honest fabric + one pearl of light regardless of the agenda. Anchor these ordinary hours in cool tones like stark navy and icy grey. Combine a matt worsted wool trouser with technical nylon outerwear. Mix your metals freely. Slip a silver ring next to a gold watch. Test the resistance of every garment against your skin. If a silhouette collapses on the body, take it off immediately.",
      "sectionIntro": "Establish a strict baseline for ordinary mornings.",
      "tests": [
