      "text": "Pick up the {metal_1} chain or {stone_1} pendant and drop it into your palm. Rely on this undeniable heft to ground the delicate float of weightless layers. Deliberately aged bronze, pounded copper, and artificial tarnish register as visual noise against a cool aesthetic. Reject them. Bring your focus to high-shine rhodium, smooth white gold, and mirror-polished steel. A heavy, bright zipper pull or dense metal clasp provides the strict anchor required to pull a fluid garment into sharp relief.",
