    },
    "accessory_2": {
      "text": "Choose a technical nylon crossbody to ground garments built on expansive colour. Inspect the hardware before you buy. Mix your metals freely. Look for matt brushed metal zips paired with one polished ring in a warm tone. Test the capacity limits directly. Fill the bag entirely and sling it across your body. If the hardware clanks loudly or the zips snag against your ribs, the bag is overdesigned. Drop it immediately. Select hardware that secures the structure rather than overwhelming the fabric. Trust your hands. The nylon must yield easily when you crush it.",
      "sectionIntro": "Demand utility and tactical precision from your everyday bags.",
      "rankedItems": [
