    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Select medium full-grain leather belts featuring a strictly matt buckle. These anchor fluid mobile layers without catching unnecessary glare. Limit keepsake jewellery to oxidised aged silver. The darkened metal sinks into warm textiles rather than shouting over them. Before leaving the house, apply the surface test. Look at your reflection and assess the entire silhouette. If any single metal clasp or ring appears visually disconnected from the fabric beneath it, take it off. Every accessory must sink into the visual current, serving as your one warm point of light, never hovering above it.",
      "sectionIntro": "Secure the final functional elements to ground the silhouette.",
