      ]
    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Treat a morning run to the greengrocer as a definite event. Do not drop your standards just because the errand is small. Buying ibuprofen at the local chemist does not excuse sloppy choices. Build the outfit. Pull on a heavy cashmere knit in warm, rich toffee. Clasp a matt brass watch to your wrist. Test the density of the fabric before you step outside. Substantial material drapes correctly. Your baseline equation never wavers. It is always structure + athletic space + a touch of quiet depth. Notice the raw contrast of brushed camel wool over sturdy denim. Rely on the solid cut of full-grain leather boots to dictate your stride. Dress for the mundane with absolute intention.",
      "sectionIntro": "Enforce your baseline daily without negotiation.",
      "tests": [
