      "text": "Lift {stone_1} and {stone_2} directly from the tray. Assess their undeniable physical mass to verify quality. Highly faceted, gleaming gems flash distractingly beside warm, muted garments. Stick to smooth, cabochon or tumbled textures to keep your combinations cohesive. Opaque minerals introduce a touch of quiet depth to your wardrobe. Demand stones that bring dense, literal weight to your body. Let their natural, unpolished state ground your athletic space.",
