    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Your garments build the required structure and define your athletic space. Your accessories exist strictly to introduce a touch of quiet depth. Apply a rigorous filter here. Limit yourself to a handful of strong functional items per look. Begin this process with your daily carry. Demand full-grain leather bags that hold a firm, undeniable shape over time. Inspect the closures and strap buckles closely. Accept only brushed matt hardware cast in warm bronze or muted brass.",
