    "accessory_2": {
      "text": "Gather the scarf and test the fine wool or cashmere in your grip. Rely on this physical feedback. Your body recognises true substance instantly. Seek out a completely matt finish in deep rust or dark tan. This muted quality absorbs light, providing a touch of quiet depth without disrupting your athletic space. Put the wrap on, then evaluate the balance. If the textile competes with your dominant warm metals, strip the weaker item away. A single anchoring element always provides the necessary structure.",
