    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Fasten a belt of thick full-grain leather, demanding an entirely matt buckle to ground your structure. Keep your keepsake jewellery strictly within your warm palette, favouring aged brass or antiqued yellow gold. Turn the pendants over and inspect the heavily oxidised crevices. These dark recesses grant a touch of quiet depth. Meanwhile, the supple leather guarantees enough athletic space for unimpeded movement. Conclude with the subtraction test. Stare down your reflection and pinpoint the single item fighting for dominance. Unclasp the one accessory that shouts above the rest, and abandon it in the tray.",
