    "pattern_narrative": {
      "text": "Build your combinations around low-contrast tonal weaves. Tailored coats and trousers anchor {recommended_pattern_1} perfectly inside their firm structure. Fluid garments demand subtle treatments like {recommended_pattern_2} to protect their athletic space. Keep the contrast strictly low to maintain a touch of quiet depth. Ensure every motif melts seamlessly into a warm, matt background. Leave high-contrast {avoid_pattern_1} on the rack. Pass over heavy stripes, repeating logos, and harsh geometric prints that disrupt the cohesion of the cloth.",
      "sectionIntro": "Assess every pattern by its ability to act as a solid.",
