    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Treat picking up a prescription at the local chemist with the same rigorous standard you apply to a closed-door board meeting. Slipping out in the early morning frost to walk the dog requires a structured boiled wool coat in pewter grey. Do not resort to discarded loungewear. Your daily routine demands a strict foundation of neutral tones and matt surfaces. Build every morning outfit on the equation of precise fit + sensory comfort + one meticulous detail. Layer a breathable lambswool jumper over a washed silk shirt. Fasten a white gold watch. Maintain your own private baseline.",
