    },
    "accessory_2": {
      "text": "Layer fine jewellery by combining pale gold and cool silver. Seek out mixed finishes for every piece to execute one clever contrast. Pair a highly polished silver chain with a brushed matt gold ring. Grip the metal to gauge its density and let the cold weight dictate your selections. Demand crisp separation between every band and pendant. Perform a ruthless final check at the door. Scan the mirror right before you leave and take off one item if the metallic highlights blur into a confused mass. Retain only the sharp edges that cut clearly against your skin.",
