    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Select a small structured bag in kid suede or smooth leather. A rigid top-handle creates crisp separation against your worsted wool outerwear, guaranteeing sharp edges. Look for fine mixed hardware that combines cool silver and pale gold components to add one clever contrast. Pick the bag up and check the density of the clasp. Trust your hands to judge the construction. Before stepping out, evaluate the geometry of your layers. If a competing texture or a stray strap blurs the structural outline, leave the item behind.",
      "sectionIntro": "Apply rigorous physical standards to the items you carry and memorise the final check before stepping out.",
      "rankedItems": [
