    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "Let enduring structure lead your working day. A tailored boiled wool jacket sets the strict exterior boundary. Give the outfit internal movement with a washed silk blouse in bitter chocolate. Judge these garments blindly. Digital images manipulate reality, whereas the physical density of heavy silk crepe provides absolute certainty. Never accept a lesser standard when your primary pieces undergo maintenance. If your dark mahogany trousers sit at the tailor, refuse to downgrade to a stiff polyester substitute just to get through the week. Demand a strictly warm palette and a matt finish across all your items. Mix your metals quietly on a watch bezel or shoe hardware.",
