    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, soft shelter takes precedence. Build a stark navy foundation using worsted wool. Support this base with fluid mobility. A crisp cotton poplin shirt in icy grey provides structural ease. Ground the outfit with a personal matt silver watch. Apply your test daily. Processing a mundane invoice does not require collapsing your outline into shapeless merino. Retain your crisp edges regardless of the task. Keep your palette distinctly cool.",
      "sectionIntro": "Master your daily professional uniform by establishing clear physical boundaries.",
      "tests": [
