    },
    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "Treat a mundane errand as an extension of your baseline. Collecting dry cleaning does not require abandoning your silhouette. Maintain your cool, muted palette even for minor tasks. Reach for a stark navy poplin overshirt or worsted wool trousers instead of shapeless leisurewear. Your standard must remain absolute. Anchor every weekday choice to your exact equation of soft shelter + light movement + one sentimental keepsake. The quiet discipline of technical nylon paired with icy grey cotton prepares you for unpredictable weather without restricting your stride. Choose garments that allow rapid adaptation.",
      "sectionIntro": "Approach your everyday clothing as an active baseline.",
      "tests": [
