    "hardware_stones": {
      "text": "Your hardware must anchor the light movement in your garments. Pass over any stone or setting mimicking antiquity. They read as historical clutter against a present-tense aesthetic. Rely instead on mirror-polished cool hardware to maintain a sharp boundary. Gauge the stone by its physical heft. A weighty mineral provides a necessary counterweight to your soft shelter. Choose pieces that offer a muted reality over high-gloss faceting. Look for the matt opacity of {stone_1} or the dense core of {stone_2}. These solid materials reinforce your self-contained orientation.",
