    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Accessories supply the one sentimental keepsake to complete your soft shelter and your light movement. Restrict your hardware to one or two strong pieces per look. Start with a watch. Look for a brushed steel case on a leather or steel strap, ensuring the cool metal holds a flat matt brushed surface. Test the mechanics of every addition. Engage the clasp and feel the resistance. If the dial is illegible or the buckle slips, reject the piece entirely. Rely on direct physical feedback to decide what touches your skin.",
