    "accessory_1": {
      "text": "Accessories deliver the one refined touch that finalises your shape. Build your base carefully to maintain balanced proportions, and ensure the resulting silhouette retains its light movement. Confine your additions to one or two strong pieces per look. Begin with eyewear. Search for an acetate frame with a mixed finish. Blend polished curves with matt edges in cool hues. Put the piece through the mechanical test immediately. Open and close the arms rapidly. If the hinges stick or the plastic rattles, drop it. Trust the construction above the brand name. The engineering must support daily wear.",
      "sectionIntro": "Select your finishing elements to ground your physical presence.",
