      ]
    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Finish your outfit with a clean leather boot. Pick it up and inspect the sole. Avoid heavy treads that drag on the pavement. Select a sleek calfskin profile to preserve balanced proportions from head to toe. A polished steel zip alongside a matt silver buckle integrates perfectly into your cool palette. Run the stride test before you leave. Walk rapidly across the room. If the boot pinches your heel or restricts light movement, take it off immediately. Do not wear shoes that force you to adjust your natural gait.",
      "sectionIntro": "Evaluate your final accessories through the strict lens of physical utility.",
