    "textures_bad": {
      "text": "Deploy friction to protect your cool equilibrium. Press the material to the sensitive inner skin of your arm. If {texture_bad_1} scratches or drags, drop the garment immediately. Notice how {texture_bad_2} stifles the skin and stiffens your movement. These rigid options destroy your baseline comfort. Your aesthetic relies on precise choices, creating space for one pearl of light to draw the eye. A dull, matt {texture_bad_3} will only generate tactile noise. Trust your nerve endings. Appearance is an illusion. A harsh scrape against bare skin delivers the unvarnished reality.",
      "sectionIntro": "Train your hands to reject materials that fight the skin.",
      "tests": [
        "the wrist test"
      ]
    },
    "textures_sweet_spot": {
      "text": "Your best material tension happens when {sweet_spot_keyword_1} meets {sweet_spot_keyword_2}. This exact pairing creates your required cool composure. Pick up the items and test the blend by sliding both weaves across your collarbone. If either thread irritates your pulse point, drop the piece immediately. Rely entirely on physical touch to judge quality. Photography obscures flaws, but pure drape exposes every structural shortcut. Bring in {texture_good_1} at the neckline to act as one pearl of light above the matt finishes below.",
      "sectionIntro": "Combine finishes to build your central material tension.",
      "tests": [
        "the wrist test"
      ]
    },
    "palette_narrative": {
      "text": "Your temperature is cool. Construct your base from {core_colour_1}, {core_colour_2}, and {core_colour_3}. Deploy {core_colour_4} as your neutral substitute. Add {accent_colour_1} or {accent_colour_2} as a single deliberate accent. Integrate the relief tone sparingly to break up dark stretches. Watch out for the all-earth sink. Piling {core_colour_1} on {core_colour_3}, all matt and dense, can swallow you whole. Lift this trap by placing {core_colour_4} at the collar, adding one piece of polished full-grain leather, or bringing in the relief tone. Bypass severe saturated red, stark optic white, and harsh neon. These tones fracture your cool composure.",
