    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At the desk, let weightless layers take the lead. Build an inky navy foundation in matt silk, and support it with a structured dove grey brushed wool jacket. Drafting a routine email does not require collapsing your silhouette. Maintain a sharp shape even during mundane tasks. Allow a cool steadiness to ground this physical lightness. Anchor your base with deep teal full-grain leather footwear. Finish with a solitary silver cuff. This single point of illumination provides sharp visual focus without creating unnecessary noise.",
