      ]
    },
    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Lift the {metal_1} off the display and weigh it in your palm. Base your assessment purely on this physical heft. Assess the surface immediately after. High-gloss polished finishes will clash aggressively with soft muted colours. A highly reflective edge shatters the visual cohesion of your warm palette. Seek out matt and brushed textures instead. A heavy brushed buckle or a dense matt clasp secures your close drape without distraction. Let this subtle finish maintain the quiet undercurrent you require.",
      "sectionIntro": "Subject every metal component to a strict physical evaluation before you commit to wearing it.",
      "tests": [
