    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Anchor your waist with wide full-grain leather belts featuring a matt brushed warm brass buckle. This grounds the silhouette while maintaining a close drape across the torso. For keepsake jewellery, select a deep garnet or amber stone set in oxidised brass or aged silver. Apply the Single Weight Test before leaving. Scan your reflection, isolate the heaviest item, and remove it. If a heavy amber ring fights your wide leather belt for attention, take the ring off. Your quiet undercurrent demands singular focus, not a chorus of distractions.",
      "sectionIntro": "Edit your final accents ruthlessly to protect the visual silence of your silhouette.",
      "rankedItems": [
