    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, let structure lead. The sharp cut of a heavy wool blazer sets a firm boundary. Let sensory comfort and a touch of quiet depth provide the support. A cashmere roll-neck establishes a warm foundation. A matt gold collar pin and a rich toffee leather briefcase anchor the look. Maintain absolute discipline with professional attire. Feel the density of the weave before selecting anything for the office. If a jacket feels thin or hollow, leave it on the rack. The heft of your garments conveys authority far better than superficial styling.",
