    "occasions_intimate": {
      "text": "In low light, sensory comfort leads. Close quarters reward warm, tactile fibres that invite proximity. Pair a matt silk blouse in rich toffee with a camel brushed wool skirt. Choose muted yellow gold jewellery that gives a soft glow. Evaluate these evening pieces purely by touch. A heavy cashmere wrap and full-grain leather boots provide reliable elegance without requiring adjustment. Avoid stiff synthetics that fail under close inspection. Rely instead on soft, balanced tailoring that moves seamlessly with you, ensuring every layer holds its own integrity.",
