    "occasions_daily": {
      "text": "A morning walk to the sorting office is no excuse to drop your standards. Rely on structure + sensory comfort + a touch of quiet depth to dictate every outfit. Construct daytime looks from thick camel cashmere and rich toffee full-grain leather. Evaluate the drape of a matt silk blouse in natural light. If the material clings poorly, discard it. Select brushed wool trousers that maintain their crisp lines while remaining soft on the skin. Assess the metals on your belt buckles and ensure they remain strictly warm and muted. Never compromise this standard for mere convenience.",
