    "hardware_stones": {
      "text": "Require opaque, dense stones that absorb rather than reflect the ambient light. Select {stone_1} or {stone_2} to bring necessary structure to your jewellery collection. Lift every piece off the velvet tray before purchasing to gauge its true substance. The stone must possess enough density to anchor the design. Glassy gems create a sharp, distracting clash next to your soft, muted garments. Reject these icy finishes. Set your stones in brushed or matt metals to maintain a cohesive, warm palette.",
