    "hardware_tip": {
      "text": "Close your hand around the metal. A substantial clasp or chain provides the only reliable measure of quality. Harsh, polished hardware creates a glaring distraction against muted, warm garments. Reject the glare. Demand a deeply brushed or matt surface for your {metal_1}. This subdued finish anchors the piece with definitive shape. It ensures the quiet depth of your wardrobe remains completely intact.",
