    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Anchor your outfit with a medium full-grain leather belt in rich toffee, securing the fabric with a simple matt buckle to establish firm proportions. Incorporate keepsake jewellery crafted from oxidised, aged silver. This intentionally tarnished metal brings a touch of quiet depth to your warm foundation. Test the physical weight of these final additions to verify their absolute quality. Face the mirror and execute a strict subtraction test. Take off the heavy earring or the rigid cuff that clutters the neckline. A solo distinct accent carries the entire composition.",
