    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Treat everyday jewellery as a private anchor. Source pieces cast in aged brass with a singular molten gold accent. Choose a mixed finish that places raw matt surfaces next to polished edges. These warm metals settle against the skin and add hidden depth to your foundation. Weigh the brass object in your palm. If the item dictates the drape of your collar or catches too much ambient light, remove it. True quiet grandeur stays close to the body.",
      "sectionIntro": "Secure your final layer with personal objects and apply the ultimate measure of restraint.",
