      ]
    },
    "accessory_3": {
      "text": "Provide enduring structure with a wide full-grain leather belt. Inspect the hardware before putting it on. The metal must offer a matt brushed buckle rather than a high shine. For keepsake jewellery, select a deep stone set in aged silver or oxidised brass. Pick the object up and weigh it in your palm. If the piece lacks dense mass, put it down. Before stepping out, ensure only one solitary point of warm heat glows against your muted fabrics. If a second metal or stone tries to catch fire, strip it away. Keep the focus entirely self-contained.",
      "sectionIntro": "Select your final hardware and apply a strict boundary to your focal points.",
      "rankedItems": [
        {
          "name": "Belts",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "wide full-grain leather, matt brushed buckle"
        },
        {
          "name": "Keepsake jewellery",
          "role": "accessory category",
          "useCase": "deep stone set in aged silver or brass, oxidised"
