    "occasions_work": {
      "text": "At work, structure leads. Build your outfit around a camel brushed wool blazer or crisp trousers. Let the tailoring hold your shape. Clearing your inbox does not require abandoning your form for a shapeless pullover. Once you establish the rigid lines, introduce a rich toffee silk blouse or a fine cashmere crewneck to provide softness. This yielding layer sits close to the body. Finish the outfit with a touch of quiet depth. Add a matt gold signet ring next to a brushed silver cuff. These heavy, warm pieces anchor the garments.",
